---
title: Cal Smart Herby Pork Chops with Quick Apple Chutney and Smashed Potatoes
description: Sweet apples and tangy cranberries are a perfect match for tender pork chops. This fresh, DIY chutney is full of bright flavours, both sweet and savoury!

